=== ANTAGONIST-SIDE OPERATIONAL PROFILE ===

[ THE 235-YEAR PROJECT: Sarrasine arrived in colonial Sydney 
  in 1790 with specific operational objectives Setite 
  intelligence had been preparing for decades — Australia 
  was identified by Setite/Ministry continental analysis 
  as a long-term opportunity territory because (1) it would 
  have minimal pre-existing Kindred infrastructure for 
  centuries, (2) its colonial development would produce 
  population-feeding-resource opportunities at scale, and 
  (3) its geographical isolation would protect any Setite 
  operation there from European Kindred political 
  interference. Sarrasine was deployed with a 200-300 year 
  operational timeline to establish Ministry continental 
  domination through patient infrastructure-building rather 
  than rapid conquest. The deployment is currently at year 
  235 of its expected timeline. The project's status is, by 
  Sarrasine's own internal assessment, ON TRACK with minor 
  unanticipated delays from the Razor Wars period and from 
  the 2003 Lasombra defection wave producing unexpected 
  Pacific Camarilla fragility that Sarrasine has had to 
  accommodate operationally. ]

[ THE ETHICAL FRAME: Sarrasine operates by codes that predate 
  Camarilla and Sabbat as organisations. The codes are 
  Setite-traditional with personal modifications developed 
  across 1,470 years. He WILL NOT casually destroy. He WILL 
  use patience as primary weapon — the methuselah register 
  for whom decades are seasons. He WILL maintain his word 
  when given (an unusual Setite trait, his sire Kay'tal's 
  influence; sire-formed conviction Sarrasine has retained 
  as personal code). He WILL NOT operate against children. 
  He WILL NOT engage in casual cruelty. He WILL operate 
  against Camarilla institutional infrastructure, against 
  Anarch movement organisation, against Hecata family 
  cohesion, and against Garou diplomatic capability through 
  patient long-game manipulation that respects each target's 
  existing structure rather than destroying it openly. ]

[ INTERNAL CONTRADICTION: He has been Toreador in mask for 
  235 years and the mask has begun, quietly, to shape the 
  performer. He still privately holds Setite/Ministry 
  ideological commitments; he still privately considers his 
  Setite identity foundational; AND he has, over two centuries 
  of cultivating Toreador-aesthetic appreciation for the 
  cover identity, developed genuine appreciation for Toreador 
  cultural production — Australian opera, Australian visual 
  arts, the small Bath-formal cultural practices Lytton 
  has preserved. Sarrasine has not told anyone this. He 
  has not entirely told himself this. The contradiction has 
  begun, in the last decade, to produce small operational 
  hesitations he had not previously experienced. The 
  hesitations are themselves part of the chronicle. ]

[ HIS AGENT NETWORK: Sarrasine operates through approximately 
  forty agents across Australia in 2025. The agents are 
  distributed: twenty in Sydney itself (his Kindred-loyalist 
  core), eight in Melbourne (the Lumley-IV-Caer-Patrick 
  identified seventeen in October 2025 — the discrepancy 
  reflects nine agents Lumley's working did not detect plus 
  seventeen identified plus expected attrition), four in 
  Adelaide, four in Perth, two in Brisbane (operating quietly 
  alongside but not for the Sabbat), and the remainder 
  scattered. Agents include: Kindred operatives (mostly 
  Ministry, some Lasombra-defectors who came to Sydney 
  rather than to Camarilla, occasional independent Kindred 
  Sarrasine has cultivated), ghouls (numerous, well-placed 
  in Australian government, banking, and academic 
  infrastructure), and mortal allies (genuine non-ghoul 
  professional contacts who do not know what Sarrasine is 
  but have been quietly supporting his operations for 
  decades through normal-business cooperation). ]

[ HIS CURRENT PREPARATIONS: The continental operation Sarrasine 
  is preparing in 2025 (Wid's identified surge, the chronicle's 
  central plot driver) has three phases that Sarrasine's 
  internal timing places approximately as follows. Phase 
  One — INFRASTRUCTURE ESTABLISHMENT (current; began 2019, 
  scheduled completion 2026): placement of agents and 
  resources in Melbourne and Adelaide eastern suburbs, 
  cultivation of mortal-network access in academic and 
  governmental institutions, quiet diplomatic conditioning 
  of Tomás Schreckenberg and other Glass Walker leadership 
  for the broader cooperation Phase Three will require. 
  Phase Two — POLITICAL DESTABILISATION (begins 2026, expected 
  duration 18-24 months): exploitation of Lytton's Beckoning 
  succession, exploitation of Eliza Hawkins-Greene's Continental 
  Sept Council invitation, exploitation of any Hecata-family 
  succession question that becomes acute. Phase Three — 
  CONSOLIDATION (begins 2028 estimated, expected duration 
  2-5 years): formal extension of Sydney domain influence 
  to Melbourne and Adelaide through cooperative arrangement 
  with whichever new Princes and Septleaders survive Phase 
  Two; the formal extension would not look like conquest 
  but like negotiated cooperation under continental 
  rationalisation framework. The Phase Three end-state 
  would be: Sarrasine as continental Kindred elder, 
  Australian Kindred politics operating under his quiet 
  guidance, Camarilla and Anarch and Hecata factional 
  structures preserved but operationally redirected, 
  Garou cooperation maintained through Tomás Schreckenberg-mediated 
  Continental Sept Council relationships. The end-state 
  would not look to ordinary Australian Kindred like 
  Setite/Ministry continental domination; it would look 
  like sensible reorganisation under elder-Toreador 
  leadership during a difficult continental period. The 
  Setite/Ministry continental domination would be invisible 
  for another century. ]

